vars {
}
NPCName "Jedrek"
Location "Sandover"
Description "Trader"
Unknown_Desc "You see a wealthy looking man in his thirties."
Known_Desc "It's Jedrek. He looks bored in his wealthy sort of way."
Detailed_Desc ""
/* Regular nodes */

Node "Jedrek_0"
notes "Generate the variable Jedrek_Temper and give it the value 0. This is referred to regularly in the dialogue."
{
NPCText "- Starting conditions for the conversation with Jedrek -"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- The player has never spoken to Jedrek before -" linkto "Jedrek_1a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- The player has spoken to Jedrek before -" linkto "Jedrek_1b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_1a_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*The well-travelled looking man looks you up and down with little interest* Yeah? And what do you want?"
 NPCFemaleText "*The well-travelled looking man looks you up and down with a dirty leer* Hey there. What can Jedrek do you for?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_GOOD playertext "Hey there, friend. My name's <PC>" linkto "Jedrek_1a_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_GOOD Gender=FEMALE playertext "Well, aren't you the baddest thing I've seen in fifty miles? What's YOUR name, caravan man?" linkto "Jedrek_1a_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hi. What's your story?" linkto "Jedrek_1a_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "How about you take a long hike without some Rad-X, asshole?" linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who you, funny man?" linkto "Jedrek_1D_1"  notes "Dumb player option."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry, I can't stop to talk. I'll see you around." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_1a_2a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well, howdy, <PC>. The name's Jedrek. It's good to meet a civ-il-ized face out here amongst all the savages. This here's the Crossroads-Sandover caravan and, for my sins, I run the operation."
 NPCFemaleText "Well, pretty lady, the name's Jedrek and the pleasure is all mine, let me tell you that. This here's the Crossroads-Sandover caravan and, for my sins, I run the operation."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_GOOD playertext "Good to meet you too, Jedrek. Can I have a look at your wares?" linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "For your sins? You're not happy on this route? What's wrong with it?" linkto "Jedrek_5_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Crossroads? Where's that?" linkto "Jedrek_4a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, good luck. I haven't got all day to stand around talking. Be seeing you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_1a_2b_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I don't go giving my name to no-one before they give me theirs. What do they call you, stranger?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_GOOD playertext "All this travelling has worn my manners down. Sorry, friend, my name's <PC>. Pleasure to meet you." linkto "Jedrek_1a_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm <PC>. How about you?" linkto "Jedrek_1a_2b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "If both of us had that attitude, we'd never get introduced, would we? Nevermind. My name's <PC>" linkto "Jedrek_1a_2b_2"  notes "Increment Jedrek_Temper by 1."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "I don't have to take this shit from a nobody like you. It's about time someone showed you some manners!" linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, look, I can't stand around talking all day. Be seeing you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_1a_2b_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "And I'm Jedrek. Well, then, <PC>, are we going to stand around all day smooth-talking each other, or do you want to trade?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sure, let's have a look at what you've got." linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Come to think of it, I've got other things to do. Be seeing you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_1b"
notes "This node begins the conversation when Jedrek and the player already know each other by name. (ie: Jedrek_2a OR Jedrek_2b_2 have been run in previous conversation)"
{
NPCText "Hello, again, <PC>. What can I do you for?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hi, Jedrek. Can I take a look at your wares?" linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hi, Jedrek. I need to ask you about something." linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Listen, Jedrek. I've been speaking to Alexander and he's told me you've been overcharging Sandover for your goods. By a long way." linkto "Jedrek_8a_1"  notes "This option only appears once the player has spoken to Alexander about Jedrek's exorbitant prices. If the PC has already tried to convince Jedrek to ply another trade route and failed, go to Jedrek 8b_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Piss off, idiot." linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes "If Jedrek_Temper>3, go to Jedrek_7_2 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hi, Jedrek. Just saying hello. See you around." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_1D_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I'm sorry?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tee hee!" linkto "Jedrek_1D_2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Leave*" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_1D_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Ah, for crying out loud. Don't these people have someone to look after you? *He looks around desperately at the Scab population*"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Will you look after me?" linkto "Jedrek_1D_3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_1D_3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*He shakes his head at you and talks far too loudly* I not help you! You must go away now!"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Sob*" linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Blow raspberry*" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_2_1a"
notes "VARIABLE = 2 * [Jedrek_Temper+1] * [1/PC Barter skill]. Divide the final sum by half IF the PC is female AND Jedrek has spoken node Jedrek_1_2a. Set a minimum value of 1 in case the PC has a very high barter skill. Maybe set a maximum price of 50 caps, in case Jedrek_Temper gets very high.\nThe barter skill, as mentioned above, is expressed as a percentage, so a skill of 75% would equal a value of 0.75."
{
NPCText "Talk in the wastes ain't cheap. *VARIABLE CAPS* and I'll tell you what you need."
 NPCFemaleText "Talk in the wastes ain't cheap, lady. *VARIABLE CAPS* and I'll tell you what you need."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Here's your money." linkto "Jedrek_2_2a"  notes "Subtract the appropriate amount from the PC's caps.\n\nIF the PC cannot pay, go instead to Jedrek_2_2d."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll pay you half that." linkto "Jedrek_2_2a"  notes "Barter check.\nIf the PC succeeds, subtract the appropriate amount from the PC's caps. Round up the halving of the amount of caps.\nIF the PC succeeds but cannot pay, go instead to Jedrek_2_2d.\nIf the PC fails, go to Jedrek_2_2b instead.\n"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "But I could just ask someone else for free!" linkto "Jedrek_2_2c"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I need to sell something to you to make the money. Let's trade." linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No deal. Be seeing you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_2_1b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Have one on the house! *He gives a wry grin*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I have a look at your wares?" linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about your companions?" linkto "Jedrek_3_0"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where does your caravan route run?" linkto "Jedrek_4_0"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Listen, Jedrek. I've been speaking to Alexander and he's told me you've been overcharging Sandover for your goods. By a long way." linkto "Jedrek_8a_1"  notes "This option only appears once the player has spoken to Alexander about Jedrek's exorbitant prices. If the PC has already tried to convince Jedrek to ply another trade route and failed, go to Jedrek 8b_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Do you want to tell me why you're such an asshole?" linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Come to think of it, I think we've covered everything. 'Bye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
