notes ""
{
NPCText "Done. What do you need to know?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I have a look at your wares?" linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about your companions?" linkto "Jedrek_3_0"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where does your caravan route run?" linkto "Jedrek_4_0"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Listen, Jedrek. I've been speaking to Alexander and he's told me you've been overcharging Sandover for your goods. By a long way." linkto "Jedrek_8a_1"  notes "This option only appears once the player has spoken to Alexander about Jedrek's exorbitant prices. If the PC has already tried to convince Jedrek to ply another trade route and failed, go to Jedrek 8b_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Do you want to tell me why you're such an asshole?" linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes "If Jedrek_Temper>3, go to Jedrek_7_2 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Come to think of it, I think we've covered everything. 'Bye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_2_2b"
notes "*VARIABLE* is the sum quoted previously, in Jedrek_2_1. Increment Jedrek_Temper by 1."
{
NPCText "I could be selling my wares instead of talking to you. *VARIABLE* caps, or no deal."
 NPCFemaleText "No offence, lady, but I could be selling my wares instead of talking. *VARIABLE* caps, or no deal."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fair enough. Here's your money." linkto "Jedrek_2_2a"  notes "Subtract the appropriate amount, as quoted in quoted previously in I could be selling my wares instead of talking to you. *VARIABLE* caps, or no deal, from the PC's caps."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "But I could just talk to someone else for free!" linkto "Jedrek_1a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I need to sell something to you to make the money. Let's trade." linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm not interested if I have to pay that much. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_2_2c"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*Jedrek looks unconcerned* Help yourself. I'm a busy man. Come back when you've got something to sell, or you want to buy."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Now you come to mention it, let's see if we can do business." linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Come on, don't be such a miserly asshole. It's important you tell me what I need to know." linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes "If Jedrek_Temper>3, go to Jedrek_7_2 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fine. I'll be off, then." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_2_2d"
notes "Increment Jedrek_Temper by 1"
{
NPCText "*Jedrek turns away* If you want talk, you better go find some work until you can afford it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me sell you some of my gear." linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How about I beat it out of you?" linkto "Jedrek_7_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be back." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_3_0"
notes ""
{
NPCText "These two? Huh. If you think it'll do you any good."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You don't sound too fond of them." linkto "Jedrek_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps I ought to ask you something else, then." linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I suppose not. Be seeing you, then." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_3a_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Them? Don't you believe it. Check Kelly out. Pretty easy on the eye, wouldn't you say, buddy?"
 NPCFemaleText "Them? Don't you believe it. Check Kelly out. Pretty girl, but her head's fulla crazy ideas about how I shout be runnin' the show. I reckon she sees herself in my shoes."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=MALE playertext "Yeah, not bad." linkto "Jedrek_3a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What about the other one, that guy over there?" linkto "Jedrek_3b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So that's Kelly. Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Look, I've got to be going. I'll see you around, Jedrek. Take it easy." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_3a_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well, that's what I thought until I worked with her a few weeks. She's one of them broads that fancies herself as kinda smart, you know? Gives them ideas. I reckon she sees herself in my shoes."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What about the other one, that guy over there?" linkto "Jedrek_3b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Could I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Look, I've got to be going. I'll see you around, Jedrek. Take it easy." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_3b_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Him? I don't even know his real name. We kinda call him Brute. You can see why."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What's his story?" linkto "Jedrek_3b_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, no. Why's that?" linkto "Jedrek_3b_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I guess so. Can I ask you about another thing?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I ought to be going. 'Bye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_3b_2a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "What the...? Because he's a muscle-bound lug is why!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see what you mean, now. So what's his story?" linkto "Jedrek_3b_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh, right. Can I ask you about another thing?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_3b_2b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "'Fore I met him, folks say he was a regular kinda guy. One night in Crossroads, though, he had one beer too many. When he went to stand up he keeled over and hit his head something terrible on the floor."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Go on..." linkto "Jedrek_3b_3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_3b_3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "He woke up the next morning and was never the same since. He's bin this surly brute to this day. Can't get a word, a joke, a smile or nothin' out of the dumb ox."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It affected him that badly?" linkto "Jedrek_3b_4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So that's Brute. Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "As much as I love a good story, I've got to be moving on. 'Bye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_3b_4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh, sure. And that's why I don't allow him to touch a drop o' booze whilst he's working for me. I reckon one beer could be enough for the same to happen again."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So that's your crew. Mind if I ask you another question?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "If you can't stand your own crew, you're an idiot for hiring them." linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes "If Jedrek_Temper>3, go to Jedrek_7_2 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Nice to meet you all. I ought to be going. 'Bye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_4_0"
notes ""
{
NPCText "This here's the Crossroads-Sandover caravan. *He frowns.* Didn't I mention that before?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about Crossroads?" linkto "Jedrek_4a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "What do you think of Sandover?" linkto "Jedrek_4b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I suppose not. See you around." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_4a_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You don't know Crossroads? *He laughs* I suppose I'm almost envious of you. It's a trading town. Run by Jack and his family. Whatever you might need, you can usually find there."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Could you please tell me how to find Crossroads?" linkto "Jedrek_4a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hey, is that the time? I ought to make a move. Be seeing you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_4a_2"
notes "VARIABLE = 5 * [Jedrek_Temper+1] * [PC Barter skill]. Divide the final sum by half IF the PC is female AND Jedrek has spoken node Jedrek_1_2a. Round up the final value to avoid a value of 0 caps. Maybe set a maximum price of 50 caps, in case Jedrek_Temper gets very high.\nThe barter skill, as mentioned above, is expressed as a percentage, so a skill of 75% would equal a multiplier of 0.75."
{
NPCText "Now that's going to cost you. *VARIABLE* caps."
 NPCFemaleText "Now that's going to cost you. Sorry, lady. *VARIABLE* caps."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Here's your money." linkto "Jedrek_4a_3a_1"  notes "Subtract the appropriate amount from the PC's caps.\n\nIF the PC cannot pay, go instead to BLAGH"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll pay you half that and not a cap more." linkto "Jedrek_4a_3a_1"  notes "Barter check.\nIf the PC succeeds, subtract the appropriate amount from the PC's caps.\nIF the PC succeeds but cannot pay, go instead to BLAGH.\nIf the PC fails, go to Jedrek_4a_3b instead.\n"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "But I could just ask someone else for free!" linkto "Jedrek_4a_3c"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Talk to me about Sandover instead." linkto "Jedrek_4b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I need to sell something to you to make the money. Let's trade." linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Forget it. Let me ask you something else instead." linkto "Jedrek_2_2a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_4a_3a_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Done. Now, take a look at this. *He uses a stick to draw a map in the sand at his feet*. Now this here's Sandover, see? That's where we are. That's north that way, by the way..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "OK, with you so far." linkto "Jedrek_4a_3a_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_4a_3a_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "...Now this down here is Crossroads. Heh - and this here in between the two is the same goddamn route I been runnin' for as long as I can remember."
 NPCFemaleText "...Now this down here is Crossroads. Heh - and this here in between the two is the same goddamn route I been runnin' for as long as I can remember. Sorry, lady. I gotta stop my cussin'."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're not happy on this route? What's wrong with it?" linkto "Jedrek_5_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Jedrek, could I tag along with your caravan, next time you make the run?" linkto "Jedrek_6_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Very useful, thanks. Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. I ought to make a move. Be seeing you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
