 NPCFemaleText "*Jedrek shrugs* Go ask them, then. I'm not a public information service, lady."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "At least let me ask you about something else!" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
