Node "Jedrek_4b_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Sandover? *Jedrek makes a sour face* Sooner we're done here and gone, the better."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Why don't you like it here?" linkto "Jedrek_4b_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_4b_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Place is so radioactive it practically hums. Takes it's toll on the populace, in case you hadn't noticed."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, I can't say I had noticed." linkto "Jedrek_4b_3a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If it's so radioactive, why do you come here?" linkto "Jedrek_4b_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Radioactive? No one told me! Sell me some Rad-X, quickly!" linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_4b_3a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Let's just say you better not make any ee-motional attachments to anyone here. They tend not to last long."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "If it's so radioactive, why do you come here?" linkto "Jedrek_4b_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It's that live here? I need to buy some anti-rad drugs from you now!" linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about Crossroads?" linkto "Jedrek_4a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_2a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_4b_3b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Don't worry about me, buddy. I make sure me 'n' Kelly have plenty enough Rad-X. Brute don't like the medicine, so I crumble it up and put it in his food when he ain't lookin'."
 NPCFemaleText "Don't worry about me, lady. I make sure me 'n' Kelly have plenty enough Rad-X. Brute don't like the medicine, so I crumble it up and put it in his food when he ain't lookin'."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What effect does the radiation have on local people?" linkto "Jedrek_4b_3a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'd better have some off you, too. And quickly!" linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What's Crossroads like?" linkto "Jedrek_4a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I talk to you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_2a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_5_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Sure I ain't cheap. Why the hell should I be?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Aren't you worried someone else will undercut you?" linkto "Jedrek_5_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't know. Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_5_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "No other caravans come by this way. I got me a monopoly on this run because no-one else is dumb enough to make it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why? What's wrong with it?" linkto "Jedrek_5_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "At least business is good. Can I ask you another question?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, OK. See you around, Jedrek." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_5_3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "What's wrong with it? What's right with it is more like it. The money ain't bad, but hell, son, this is the boringest, dullest stretch of wasteland you ever did see."
 NPCFemaleText "What's wrong with it? What's right with it is more like it. The money ain't bad, but - and pardon my lingo, lady - hell, this is the boringest, dullest stretch of wasteland you ever did see."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It doesn't sound so bad if it's making you decent money." linkto "Jedrek_5_4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry to hear it. Mind if I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, I've got my problems too. See you around, Jedrek." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_5_4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "...and Sandover is dangerously radioactive."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You've got plenty of Rad-X; what's the problem?" linkto "Jedrek_5_5"  notes "Only display this node if Jedrek has spoken node Jedrek_4b_3b."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh, I can imagine how that would put other people off." linkto "Jedrek_5_5"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_5_5"
notes ""
{
NPCText "That ain't the half of it. *Jedrek leans closer and whispers conspiratorially* Between you an' me? My travelling companions leave a lot to be desired, too."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why not fire them and get another crew?" linkto "Jedrek_5_6a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So why don't you join another caravan run? There must be more, surely?" linkto "Jedrek_5_6b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Your travelling companions? Not the greatest conversationalists, then?" linkto "Jedrek_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have to be going. See you around, Jedrek." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_5_6a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Haven't you been listening? For a start, no-one else will come near Sandover on account of its radiation."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why don't you join a caravan crew running another route?" linkto "Jedrek_5_6b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Could you tell me about your current crew?" linkto "Jedrek_3_0"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about something else." linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_5_6b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Sure, there's other runs. But none of them pay so well, see? I'm a businessman before I'm a glory seeker, and this set up here at Sandover is plenty sweet enough to justify the boredom of coming here."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And your travelling companions don't liven up the journey?" linkto "Jedrek_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Have you got time for another question?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That makes sense. I must be going now, though." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_6_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You want to come along for the ride, too? *He looks you up and down again*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "- WAIT -" linkto "Jedrek_6_2a"  notes "Subtract Jedrek_Temper from Charisma and make a 1-to-10 'roll'. If failed, go to Jedrek_6_2b instead."
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_6_2a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Sure, I reckon we could handle you if you tried any smart stuff."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hey! I just want passage. I'm not going to give you any trouble." linkto "Jedrek_6_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Come to think of it, this might not be a good idea. I'll see you later." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_6_2b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "No, sorry. You can't be too careful in the wastes, as I'm sure you appreciate."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I understand. Can I ask you about something else, though?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Be like that then, you asshole." linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "OK, goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_6_3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Just as well. Besides which, if some assholes show up and try to rob us, it's always good to have another ready pair of hands."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No problem. I can take care of myself in a fight." linkto "Jedrek_6_4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sounds dangerous. I think I'll give it a miss. Although I still need to talk to you about something else." linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've changed my mind, come to think of it. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_6_4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "One other thing. Don't get no ideas about asking for pay. You look after the caravan and the caravan looks after you. That's the offer, that's the deal."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sounds fair enough. It's a deal, Jedrek." linkto "Jedrek_6_5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hmm... I'll think about it. Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Dangerous and unpaid? I think I'll leave it. Speak to you another time." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_6_5"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Great! Be here on ***DATE OF CARAVAN DEPARTURE***."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "OK. See you then, Jedrek." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be here. I've got another question, if you don't mind." linkto "Jedrek_2_1b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, I've changed my mind. See you later anyway." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_7_1"
notes "Increment Jedrek_Temper by 1"
{
NPCText "You want to re-think your words, buddy? Don't think I won't kill you if you mess with me."
 NPCFemaleText "You want to re-think your words, lady? Don't think I won't kill you if you mess with me."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Sorry, I don't know what came over me. How about I look over your goods and buy something by way of apology?" linkto "Jedrek_Trade"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Fuck you!" linkto "Jedrek_7_2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_7_2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Brute, kill this asshole."
 NPCFemaleText "Brute, kill this bitch."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let's go!" linkto "combat"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*gulp!*" linkto "combat"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8a_1"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Alexander thinks he knows the market better than me, does he?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't believe that he thinks he knows better, as such." linkto "Jedrek_8a_2b"  notes "Easy speech check. If failed, go to Jedrek_9 instead.\nWrong choice. (Defensive and weak). Punishment is another node with a speech check."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Come on, Jedrek, you know your prices are exorbitant." linkto "Jedrek_8a_2a"  notes "Easy speech check. If failed, go to Jedrek_9 instead.\nThis is the correct choice (forthright, no-nonsense). Reward is bypassing another node with a speech check. "
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8a_2a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "So I'm charging over the odds? I don't see any competition 'round here. What's it to you, anyway?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Look, I know you're only charging so highly because you hate this trade route..." linkto "Jedrek_8a_3"  notes "Easy speech check. If failed, go to Jedrek_9 instead.\nCorrect response. (Sympathetic to Jedrek's plight)."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let's just say I've a vested interest." linkto "Jedrek_8a_3"  notes "Wrong response. (Smug, ambivalent). Moderate speech test. If the PC fails, route Jedrek's response to Jedrek_9 instead."
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8a_2b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well, what then?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "He said that your prices were far too high for Sandover to afford." linkto "Jedrek_8a_2a"  notes "Easy speech check. If failed, go to Jedrek_9 instead."
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8a_3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Go on, I'm listening..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Look at the bigger picture. Your prices are killing the market in Sandover." linkto "Jedrek_8a_4"  notes "Easy speech test. If the PC fails, route Jedrek's response to Jedrek_9 instead."
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8a_4"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You think so?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I admit that I'm no expert, but yes, I do." linkto "Jedrek_8a_5b"  notes "Wrong choice. (Shows lack of experience). Punishment is another node with a speech test.\nEasy speech test. If failed, go to Jedrek_9 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The other routes are open to all sorts of opportunities for expanding your operation." linkto "Jedrek_8a_5a"  notes "Correct choice (to the point and decisive) \nEasy speech test. If the PC fails, route Jedrek's response to Jedrek_9 instead."
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8a_5a"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Mm-hmm."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "All you've got to look forward to here is an early funeral where the only mourners will be your dissatisfied customers." linkto "Jedrek_8a_6"  notes "Easy speech test at this point. If the PC fails, route Jedrek's response to Jedrek_9 instead."
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8a_5b"
notes ""
{
NPCText "So what do I do about it, if you know all the answers?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Look to the other routes. They're not so stale and worn-out." linkto "Jedrek_8a_5a"  notes "Easy speech test. If the PC fails, route Jedrek's response to Jedrek_9 instead."
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8a_6"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hell, when you put it like that... I guess you're right."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm glad you agree. What do you say?" linkto "Jedrek_8a_7"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8a_7"
notes ""
{
NPCText "OK, I need to get out of this rut... but I can't just up and leave like that to go searching for new work. It could take months, and I ain't THAT rich."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How about if I go looking for you? I've got a lot of travelling to do and could ask around as I go." linkto "Jedrek_8a_8"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, I suppose you're stuck here, then. See you around." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8a_8"
notes "The PC gains the mission where he must go to Crossroads to find a new route for Jedrek. Decrement Jedrek_Temper by 1."
{
NPCText "Shucks, would you do that for me? That'd be great."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I could tag along with you next time you go to Crossroads, maybe. Then I'd ask around whilst you were working." linkto "Jedrek_6_1"  notes "If the player clicks this option, he gets the mission to find a new trade route for Jedrek."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No problem, Jedrek. I'll ask around at my next port of call. Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1b"  notes "If the player clicks this option, he gets the mission to find a new trade route for Jedrek."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, forget it. I'm going to be too busy. See you later." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8b_1"
notes "Increment Jedrek_Temper by 1."
{
NPCText "You already talked to me about that. Don't bother me with it again."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, listen, Jedrek, you really need to hear me out." linkto "Jedrek_8a_1"  notes "Hard speech check. If failed, go to Jedrek_8b_2 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're right. Well, can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Cantankerous asshole." linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes "If Jedrek_Temper>3, go to Jedrek_7_2 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Shrug* Not my loss. Be seeing you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_8b_2"
notes "Increment Jedrek_Temper by 1"
{
NPCText "I SAID don't bother me with that crap!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Jedrek, if you'll just give me a chance..." linkto "Jedrek_8a_1"  notes "Hard speech check. If the PC fails, go to Jedrek_7_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "OK, sorry. It was worth a try. Can I still ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Don't raise your voice with me, dick-head." linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes "If Jedrek_Temper>3, go to Jedrek_7_2 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Shrug* Not my loss. Be seeing you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_9"
notes "Increment Jedrek_Temper by 1."
{
NPCText "You're in over your head, boy. Go tell it to someone who cares a damn."
 NPCFemaleText "You're in over your head, lady. Go tell it to someone who cares a damn."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh... OK. Well, can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You've got a smart mouth, Jedrek, and I've a good mind to shut it up." linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes "If Jedrek_Temper>3, go to Jedrek_7_2 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "*Shrug* Not my loss. Be seeing you." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jedrek_Trade"
notes ""
{
NPCText "*** NOTE: The trade dialogue window comes up and the player can trade. Once the player closes the window he has the following options. ***"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Woah, you certainly aren't cheap, Jedrek." linkto "Jedrek_5_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Alexander told me you were overcharging on your wares. He wasn't joking!" linkto "Jedrek_8a_1"  notes "This option only appears once the player has spoken to Alexander about Jedrek's exorbitant prices. If the PC has already tried to convince Jedrek to ply another trade route and failed, go to Jedrek 8b_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. Have you got time to answer a few questions?" linkto "Jedrek_2_1a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "I suppose you think it's funny to charge those sorts of prices, asshole." linkto "Jedrek_7_1"  notes "If Jedrek_Temper>3, go to Jedrek_7_2 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That did it for me, Jedrek. See you around." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
